IJanuaRecord.GUID Property

Summary

Contains a 128bit GUID unique identifier for the record or the Resource.

Namespace: Janua.Orm.Intf
Syntax
Delphi
public
 property GUID: TGUID read GetGUID write SetGUID;

Property Value

Type: TGUID

 

Remarks

This GUID is used as a common PK for object all around the network This allows synchronization between local and remote istances
